Author: QuijiaBored2
Text: I've been vaping for about 6 months now but never had the time as much as now so that would make sense. Thanks!

Author: skeet_yeet_repeat
Text: Nicotene is a vasoconstrictor which can have that effect. Similar to coffee. However you will build up tolerance very rapidly so it will only be noticable at first, and perhaps mildly effective if you imbibe once a day.
